title: KSL.com college football Players of the Week (Week 7)
text:
SALT LAKE CITY Â— It was a great week for local college football teams as all teams in the state won this weekend. 
BYU had another fourth-quarter rally to beat Cincinnati. Utah, too, needed a fourth-quarter rally to finally beat Arizona State after a near 40-year drought. And Utah State took it to Boise State over the weekend in a blowout victory.
